<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9675</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比跟妈妈挥手说完再见，走进了学校。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25522</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29413</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他觉得来学校有点别扭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29413</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38179</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他不是来上课，也不是来儿童中心，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42389</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>而是来儿童中心夏令营！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49642</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比在体育馆里看到了一桶水气球。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49642</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52696</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个高高的男人穿着一件T恤，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52696</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57324</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>上面写着 “儿童中心夏令营” 。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60094</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他还戴着一顶帽子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60095</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好！” 男人说，“你是波比吧？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65934</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70662</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。” 波比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73679</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您是邓恩老师吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73679</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78880</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比的妈妈说过这个夏天雪莉老师不在。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78880</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81270</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邓恩老师笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81270</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86308</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。雪莉老师是我的朋友，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86308</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90204</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她说过你会成为篮球明星。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93265</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比想笑，但忍住了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93265</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97266</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有啦。” 他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97266</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103426</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，体育馆的门开了，两个女生冲了进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103426</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“尼娜！莉琪！你们也来夏令营了？” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109463</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是啊。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118475</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很期待。” 尼娜说，“好想快点开始。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118475</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个女生咯咯笑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121460</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123910</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们看了看新老师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123910</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127510</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您好，邓恩老师。” 她们说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132883</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们好！” 邓恩老师说，“我们在等——”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132884</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137259</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“贾森和伊坦！” 莉琪大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137259</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140945</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对。” 邓恩老师很惊讶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140945</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的意思是，贾森和伊坦来了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150232</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪指了指正走过来的贾森和伊坦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156011</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太好了。贾森、伊坦，我是邓恩老师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156011</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家跟我出去吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162424</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 邓恩老师带着他们来到外面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169433</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要玩儿‘认识你’扔水气球游戏，两人一组。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169433</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪和尼娜先组成了一组。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178233</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森和伊坦组成了一组。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178233</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183349</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“波比，你可以作我的搭档吗？” 邓恩老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183349</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比开心起来。“当然可以！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196616</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们先面对面。” 邓恩老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196616</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一个人拿着气球。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199242</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204494</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>扔气球时，要说一句关于自己搭档的话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204494</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210293</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我举个例子。” 邓恩老师看着波比，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“波比喜欢篮球！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 他一边说，一边把水气球扔给波比。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220465</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比接到球。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220465</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223556</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“接到球后，往后退一步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223556</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229765</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后扔回给你的搭档，并说一句关于你搭档的话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229765</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233599</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>明白了吗？” 邓恩老师看看大家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233599</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“明白了！” 莉琪举起一个气球。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“小心，莉琪。” 尼娜说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247821</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果气球破了，我们就出局了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247821</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252063</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“尼娜说得对。” 邓恩老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252063</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257282</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“最后拿着气球的那一组就赢了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257282</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260762</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>搭档们面对面地站好了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260762</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268443</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“贾森喜欢做饭！” 伊坦大喊着把气球扔出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268443</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274079</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“伊坦喜欢大海！” 贾森把气球扔回去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274079</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“尼娜很会跳绳。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285570</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“莉琪很会逗别人笑。” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比还没有把气球扔出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不好了，邓恩老师。我不了解您啊！” 他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你一定了解一些。” 邓恩老师说，“想一想。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您骑自行车来夏令营！” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308665</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312400</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您喜欢园艺！” 伊坦说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312400</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 波比笑了。“您是雪莉老师的朋友！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>321955</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们欢呼起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>321955</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>329908</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个夏天一定会很有趣！” 波比想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>